        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Not just students who do the required reading. Who merely study for tests, and solve for symptoms.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "But students who are eager to learn about the whole problem. Who see the big picture. Who are ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "insatiably",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " curious about it.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Most importantly, what we need are people to see the limits and the edges of their knowledge. And to be absolutely resolute in their willingness to do ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "something",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " about it.",
